Package edu.monash.fit2099

Class AutoShowroom

java.lang.Object
edu.monash.fit2099.AutoShowroom
public class AutoShowroom
extends java.lang.Object
The AutoShowroom Class stores Cars and Buyers in 2 arraylists It also contains all methods used by the I/O menu These methods include creating vehicles, buyers, bids along with displaying cars and buyers
Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Enoch Leow
See Also:
Buyer, Sedan, Truck, Vehicle, SedanException, TruckException, VehicleException
